{"word":"πικραίνω","slug":"πικραίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πικραίνω</b></el> <el>(πικραίνω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πικρός'><el>πικρός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to make sharp</i> or <i>bitter</i> to the taste, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be exasperated, foster bitter feelings</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}